'eang g\'c6p n\'f7a l\'b5: d\'e7 \'ae\'f8a b\'d0 \'aeang kh\'e3c b\'bbng vi\'d6c \'can b\'d7nh s\'f7a v\'b5o mi\'d6ng b\'d0, r\'cat d\'d4 b\'de s\'c6c. T\'ad\'acng t\'f9, v\'edi t\'cbt l\'ad\'eai \'a8n \'eb tr\'ce con, c\'b6 nh\'b5 th\'ad\'eang b\'bet \'d0p \'ae\'f8a b\'d0 ph\'b6i \'a8n d\'ef \'aeang kh\'e3c ho\'c6c ch\'e4c cho b\'d0 c\'ad\'eai l\'aan \'ae\'d3 h\'b8 mi\'d6ng ra l\'b5 v\'e9i \'ae\'f3t th\'f8c \'a8n v\'b5o m\'b5 kh\'abng l\'ad\'eang h\'d5t s\'f9 nguy hi\'d3m v\'d7 s\'c6c.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \cf1 S\'c6c thu\'e8c \plain \f0 \fs26 \cf1  c\'f2ng l\'b5 v\'can \'ae\'d2 c\'c7n c\'b6nh gi\'b8c. C\'b8c b\'d0 th\'ad\'eang s\'ee u\'e8ng thu\'e8c n\'aan nhi\'d2u ph\'f4 huynh s\'e8t ru\'e9t c\'f8 \'ae\'e6 b\'f5a v\'b5o mi\'d6ng b\'d0 d\'ef \'aeang gi\'c9y kh\'e3c ho\'c6c b\'det m\'f2i b\'bet b\'d0 u\'e8ng thu\'e8c th\'cbm ch\'dd c\'e3 b\'d0 d\'ad\'edi 1 tu\'e6i u\'e8ng c\'b6 thu\'e8c vi\'aan \'94 cho mau\'93! N\'a8m 96, m\'e9t b\'d0 m\'edi 11 th\'b8ng tu\'e6i v\'b5o c\'cap c\'f8u t\'b9i BV Nhi \'ae\'e5ng 1 sau khi \'ae\'ad\'eec u\'e8ng m\'e9t vi\'aan Ampicilline con nh\'e9ng g\'a9y s\'c6c t\'bet ngh\'cfn \'ae\'ad\'eang th\'eb v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 ch\'d5t tr\'ad\'edc l\'f3c \'ae\'d5n BV.\par \'a7au l\'dfng h\'acn, l\'b5 nh\'f7ng tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep ph\'b6i ch\'d5t oan u\'e6ng v\'d7 quan ni\'d6m ch\'f7a b\'d6nh l\'b9c h\'cbu \'94 \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \cf1 \'ae\'e6 s\'b6 n\'c6n chanh\plain \f0 \fs26 \cf1 \'93 khi b\'d0 \'aeang s\'e8t cao, co gi\'cbt. Chanh nguy\'aan ch\'cat v\'edi h\'b5m l\'ad\'eeng axit xitric cao th\'d7 kh\'abng ch\'d8 g\'a9y s\'c6c m\'b5 c\'dfn g\'a9y ph\'e1ng ni\'aam m\'b9c mi\'d6ng, m\'abi b\'d0 n\'f7a.\par Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'f8a b\'d0 b\'de s\'c6c th\'ad\'eang \'ae\'ada v\'b5o c\'cap c\'f8u trong t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng t\'ddm t\'b8i, suy h\'ab h\'cap, h\'abn m\'aa v\'b5 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'f6 l\'fd c\'cap c\'f8u t\'b9i nh\'b5. N\'d5u tho\'b8t ch\'d5t c\'b8c em c\'f2ng b\'de d\'de ch\'f8ng n\'b7o n\'c6ng n\'d2... Ch\'d8 t\'ddnh ri\'aang t\'b9i Khoa C\